{"id": "art-68", "label": "Art. 68", "title": "Art. 68: Procedura de soluţionare a abţinerii sau recuzării", "slug": "art-68", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1231008335\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2694\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1231008335\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 68:\nProcedura de solu&#355;ionare a ab&#355;inerii sau recuz&#259;rii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1449912071\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2693\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1449912071\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea judec&#259;torului de\ndrepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i &#351;i a judec&#259;torului de\ncamer&#259; preliminar&#259; se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; de un judec&#259;tor de\nla aceea&#351;i instan&#355;&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_712846652\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2692\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_712846652\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea judec&#259;torului care\nface parte din completul de judecat&#259; se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; de un alt\ncomplet de judecat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_990674560\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2691\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_990674560\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea magistratului-asistent se\nsolu&#355;ioneaz&#259; de completul de judecat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_85583204\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2690\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_85583204\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea grefierului se\nsolu&#355;ioneaz&#259; de judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i\nlibert&#259;&#355;i, de judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau,\ndup&#259; caz, de completul de judecat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_706085033\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2689\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_706085033\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Solu&#355;ionarea ab&#355;inerii sau recuz&#259;rii se\nface, în cel mult 24 de ore, în camera de consiliu. Dac&#259; apreciaz&#259;\nnecesar pentru solu&#355;ionarea cererii, judec&#259;torul sau completul de\njudecat&#259;, dup&#259; caz, poate efectua orice verific&#259;ri &#351;i poate\nasculta procurorul, subiec&#355;ii procesuali principali, p&#259;r&#355;ile\n&#351;i persoana care se ab&#355;ine sau a c&#259;rei recuzare se\nsolicit&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_465167107\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2688\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_465167107\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În caz de admitere a ab&#355;inerii sau a\nrecuz&#259;rii, se va stabili în ce m&#259;sur&#259; actele îndeplinite ori\nm&#259;surile dispuse se men&#355;in.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_200656332\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2687\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_200656332\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Încheierea prin care se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259;\nab&#355;inerea ori recuzarea nu este supus&#259; niciunei c&#259;i de atac.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_874608623\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2686\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_874608623\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Când pentru solu&#355;ionarea ab&#355;inerii sau a\nrecuz&#259;rii nu poate fi desemnat un judec&#259;tor din cadrul aceleia&#351;i\ninstan&#355;e sau, în cazul instan&#355;elor organizate pe sec&#355;ii, din\ncadrul aceleia&#351;i sec&#355;ii &#351;i nici din cadrul unei sec&#355;ii cu\naceea&#351;i specializare, cererea se solu&#355;ioneaz&#259; de un\njudec&#259;tor de la instan&#355;a ierarhic superioar&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1262740186\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2685\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1262740186\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)La instan&#355;ele care nu sunt organizate pe\nsec&#355;ii, în cazul în care se admite ab&#355;inerea sau recuzarea &#351;i nu\nse poate desemna un judec&#259;tor de la instan&#355;a competent&#259; pentru\nsolu&#355;ionarea cauzei, judec&#259;torul de la instan&#355;a ierarhic\nsuperioar&#259; desemneaz&#259; o alt&#259; instan&#355;&#259; egal&#259; în\ngrad cu instan&#355;a în fa&#355;a c&#259;reia s-a formulat declara&#355;ia de\nab&#355;inere sau cererea de recuzare, din circumscrip&#355;ia aceleia&#351;i\ncur&#355;i de apel sau din circumscrip&#355;ia unei cur&#355;i de apel\nînvecinate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_626987180\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2684\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_626987180\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9<sup>1</sup>)În cazul în care se admite ab&#355;inerea\nsau recuzarea, dac&#259; instan&#355;a competent&#259; pentru solu&#355;ionarea\ncauzei este organizat&#259; pe sec&#355;ii &#351;i nu se poate desemna un\njudec&#259;tor de la sec&#355;ia corespunz&#259;toare a acestei instan&#355;e,\nsolu&#355;ionarea cauzei se realizeaz&#259; de o alt&#259; sec&#355;ie a\naceleia&#351;i instan&#355;e, care are aceea&#351;i specializare. Dac&#259; nu\nexist&#259; o sec&#355;ie cu aceea&#351;i specializare, judec&#259;torul de la\ninstan&#355;a ierarhic superioar&#259; desemneaz&#259; o alt&#259;\ninstan&#355;&#259; egal&#259; în grad cu instan&#355;a în fa&#355;a c&#259;reia\ns-a formulat declara&#355;ia de ab&#355;inere sau cererea de recuzare, din\ncircumscrip&#355;ia aceleia&#351;i cur&#355;i de apel sau din\ncircumscrip&#355;ia unei cur&#355;i de apel învecinate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1703276116\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2683\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1703276116\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (8)-(9<sup>1</sup>) se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor &#351;i în cazul solu&#355;ion&#259;rii\nab&#355;inerii sau recuz&#259;rii judec&#259;torului care face parte din\ncompletul de judecat&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}